\v 14 kuti zvizadzisike zvakarehwa naIsaya muporofita, achiti:
\v 15 Nyika yeZebhuroni nenyika yeNefitarimi, \add pa\add*nzira yegungwa, mhiri kwaJoridhani, Garirea ravahedheni;
\v 16 vanhu vakanga vagere murima vakaona chiedza chikuru; navakanga vagere panharaunda nomumumvuri worufu, chiedza chakavabudira.
\s Jesu anotanga kuparidza
\p
<<<<<<< HEAD:Matthew/4/data
\v 17 Kubva ipapo Jesu wakatanga kuparidza, nokuti: Tendeukai nokuti ushe hwokudenga hwaswedera.
\s Kudamwa kwavadzidzi vokutanga
\p
\v 18 Zvino Jesu, \add wakati\add* achifamba pagungwa reGarirea, akaona vana vomunhu mumwe vaviri, Simoni unonzi Petro naAndiriya munun'una wake vachikandira mumbure mugungwa nokuti vakanga vari varedzi.
\v 19 Akati kwavari: Nditeverei, ndigokuitai varedzi vavanhu.
\v 20 Pakarepo vakasiya mimbure vakamutevera.
\v 21 Zvino achipfuurira kubva ipapo akaona vamwe vaviri vana vemunhu umwe, Jakobho waZebhedhi naJohwani munun'una wake pamwe naZebhedhi baba vavo muchikepe, vachigadzira mimbure yavo, akavadana.
\v 22 Pakarepo vakasiya chikepe nababa vavo vakamutevera.
\s Jesu unobata munyika yeGarirea
\p
\v 23 Jesu akapota neGarirea rose achidzidzisa mumasinagoge avo. Achiparidza evhangeri youshe, achiporesa chifo choga choga nechirwere pavanhu.
\v 24 Shoko rake rikabudira kuSiria yose; vakauyisa kwaari varwere vose, vakabatwa nehosha dzamarudzi mazhinji namarwadzo, navakanga vanemweya yakaipa, navaiva nezvipusha, navakanga vakawoma mitezo; akavaporesa.
\v 25 Zvaunga zvizhinji zvikamutavera, zvaibva Garirea neDhekapori, neJerusarema, neJudhiya, nemhiri kwaJoridhani.
=======
\v 17 Kubva panguva iyoyo Jesu wakatanga kuparidza, nokuti: Tendeukai, nokuti ushe hwokudenga hwaswedera.
\s Kudamwa kwavadzidzi vokutanga
\p
\v 18 Zvino Jesu, wakati achifamba pagungwa reGarirea, akaona vana vomunhu mumwe vaviri, Simoni unonzi Petro naAndiriya munun'una wake, vachikandira mimbure mugungwa, nokuti vakanga vari varedzi.
\v 19 Akati kwavari: Nditeverei, ndigokuitai varedzi vavanhu.
\v 20 Pakarepo vakasiya mimbure vakamutevera.
\v 21 Zvino wakati apfuurira mberi akaona vamwe vaviri vana vemunhu umwe muchikepe, Jakobho mwanakomana waZebhedhi naJohwani munun'una wake, vana Zebhedhi baba vavo, vachigadzira mimbure yavo, akavadana.
\v 22 Pakarepo vakasiya chikepe nababa vavo vakamutevera.
\s Jesu unobata munyika yeGarirea
\p
\v 23 Jesu akapota neGarirea rose achidzidzisa mumasinagoge avo, achiparidza evhangeri youshe, achiporesa hosha dzamarudzi ose namarwere amarudzi ose pavanhu.
\v 24 Mukurumbira wake ukapararira kuSiria yose; vakauyisa kwaari varwere vose, vakabatwa nehosha dzamarudzi mazhinji namarwadzo, navakanga vanemweya yakaipa, navaiva nezvipusha, navakanga vakawoma mitezo; akavaporesa.
\v 25 Zvino akateverwa \add ne\add*chaunga chevanhu, vaibva Garirea, neDhekapori, neJerusarema, neJudhiya, nemhiri kwaJoridhani.
